name: Skullz Jumpz
description:
Skull is doing some ninja-lessons. Help him to jump from pole to pole. Tap on the screen to make him jump and try to land on a pole. How far can you get?
Skull Jumpz is a one touch app with a lot of fun in a nice retro style.

For the cultivated Skull-Lover out there – an other fine «Z-App» from Skullz23.
